title: Motorola V171 85 g
description:
Motorola V171 85 g


Affordability meets first-class technology with the new Motorola V171 – a value packed, voice-focused flip phone polished to perfection and designed to offer the features you need while staying on budget. While light and compact, the model V171 delivers a suite of services designed to provide connections on the go including a vibrant color display, enhanced messaging capabilities, Internet access, powerful talk and standby times, as well as preloaded games and downloadable ringtones, wallpapers and screensavers. Looking to streamline your mobile lifestyle? The Motorola V171 is an ideal solution, providing durable, yet stylish mobile communications at a budget-pleasing price. Keep on Talking The Motorola V171 lets you talk for up to 348 – 633 minutes non-stop, ensuring that you’re in touch with colleagues, friends and family. The model V171 also has up to 155 – 340 hours of stand by time so you can spend less time charging and more time talking. Best yet – this sleek sliver mobile doesn’t sacrifice its slim size to accommodate for extra battery power – it still slides perfectly into your pocket or purse. Awesome Audio Rock out to your favorite tunes when friends call thanks to high quality, downloadable musical ringtones. If it’s customization you crave, the Motorola V171 delivers with the ability to hold your own personal recording session to create one-of-a kind ringtones for mobile grooving. Time Out All work and no play = no fun. So, the Motorola V171 is packed with ways to stay entertained while on-the-go. From embedded games, to “always on” Internet access to downloadable screensavers you have all the tools you need to stay connected while having a great time. Fast Chat Chat in real-time with the Motorola V171, which offers Instant Messaging capabilities to get your point across in no time flat. Need to get in touch with a pal at work? Simply use Short Message Service (SMS) to send a message to email account with ease. And, with Enhanced Messaging Service (EMS), the Motorola V171 makes it possible to send text messages that also include animations and audio. SUMMARY OF FEATURES: -Stylish, compact flip phone -Vibrant, crisp color display capable of displaying up to 4,000 colors -Superior talk (up to 348 – 633 minutes) and standby time (up to 155 – 340 hours) -Musical ringtones come in crystal clear on a polyphonic speaker -EMS, SMS and IM features for sending text, sounds, pictures and animations -GPRS technology and WAP 1.2.1 Internet browser for immediate access to Yahoo! and Hotmail accounts, news, weather, stock prices, sports scores and more -iTAP predictive text entry in several languages for rapid messaging -Preloaded games and downloadable screensavers and wallpaper for complete personalization -Alarm clock, calculator, currency converter and stop watch features to assist in a pinch

title: Sony W850i Precious Black 5.08 cm (2") 116 g
description:
Sony W850i Precious Black 5.08 cm (2") 116 g


A Walkman® phone for your senses The W850i Walkman® phone takes you one step further in mobile music evolution. The design is triple-purpose - it's a mobile phone, it's a quality Walkman® player and it's a camera. Yet it's still sleek, elegant and compact. The W850i - a phone that touches your senses. Complete Walkman® kit Everything you need for a quality mobile music experience is included in the W850i kit. A stereo headset and a 1GB Memory Stick PRO Duo™ with room for over 1000 songs. A USB cable and music management software for easy transfer of music from CD to your phone via a PC. You organise and listen to your music with the Walkman® player 2.0. It's all in the box. Online music The Walkman® player contains a direct link to an online music store. Search, browse and audition albums and tracks. Choose and download. The PlayNow™ service allows you to download even more music - plus games, videos, images and much more. Preview before you buy. Music recognition When you're listening to the radio and you hear a song you like but you don't know what it's called, ask TrackID™. Record a few seconds of the song and use TrackID™ to send the music for recognition. In seconds, you'll have the name, artist and album in your phone. Cameras With the W850i, you always have a camera at hand to catch that special moment. The 2.0-megapixel camera includes a 4x digital zoom and a horizontal user interface. The second camera sits above the phone screen and is used for video calls. 3G speed - plus internet and email Use the W850i's 3G capabilities for fast downloads and video telephony. Browse the internet or get the latest news delivered directly to your phone via RSS feeds. The W850i also supports standard push email, a solution that allows you to receive email straight to your phone.
